anno.rna <- as.tibble(colData(rna.data) )
cbind(rna.mt, anno.rna) %>%
  ggplot(aes(V1, fill=annotation)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.01)  

  facet_grid(annotation~., scales='free_y')
